name: ASS $S_2$
description: Adams Spectral Sequence for $S_2$. The $E_2$ page was generated by Amelia Perry's resolution program, the differentials and extensions were copied from Dan Isaksen.

name: ASS $S_3$
description: Adams Spectral Sequence for $S_3$. The $E_2$ page was generated by Amelia Perry's resolution program, the differentials and extensions were extracted from Nakamura "Some differentials in the mod 3 ASS" and Ravenel's book.

name: EHP
description: EHP Spectral Sequence for $p=2$. This is based on a combination of output from Strickland's mathematica program and from Mark Behren's tables.

name: HFPSS $\mathrm{EO}(3,1)$
description: The homotopy fixed point spectral sequence for $E_2^{hC_3 \!\rtimes\, C_{4}}$ for $p=3$.

name: HFPSS $\mathrm{EO}(3,2)$
description: The homotopy fixed point spectral sequence for $E_4^{hC_3 \!\rtimes\, C_{16}}$ for $p=3$.

name: HFPSS $\mathrm{EO}(5,1)$
description: Homotopy fixed point spectral sequence for $E_{4}^{hC_5\!\rtimes\, C_{16}}$ for $p=5$.

name: HFPSS $\mathit{KO}$
description: The homotopy fixed point spectral sequence for $\mathit{KO}$.

name: SSS $K(\mathbb{F}_3,n)$
description: The Serre spectral sequence computing $\mathbb{F}_3$ cohomology of $K(\mathbb{F}_3,n-1)\to pt \to K(\mathbb{F}_3,n)$ for $n=2,3,4$ with Bockstein SS's for going up to $\mathbb{Z}_3$ coefficients.

name: SSS $K(\mathbb{Z},3)$
description: The Serre spectral sequence for integral cohomology of $\mathbb{CP}^\infty \to pt \to K(\mathbb{Z},3)$

name: Slice SS $\mathit{BP}^{((C_4\!))}\langle 1\rangle$
description: The slice spectral sequence for the $C_4$ fixed points of $\mathit{BP}^{((C_4\!))}\langle 1\rangle$

name: Slice SS $\mathit{BP}^{((C_4\!))}\langle 2\rangle$
description: The slice spectral sequence for the $C_4$ fixed points of $\mathit{BP}^{((C_4\!))}\langle 2\rangle$

name: Slice SS $\mathit{BP}^{((C_8\!))}\langle 1\rangle$
description: The slice spectral sequence for the $C_4$ fixed points of $\mathit{BP}^{((C_8\!))}\langle 1\rangle$

name: Unstable ASS $S_2$
description: Unstable Adams Spectral Sequences for 2-local $S^3$, $S^5$, $S^7$ and $S^9$. The $E_2$ page was generated by scraping the data from Tangora's book, the names for the Toda range classes I got from Strickland's program, and I guessed a few differentials.
